{"tid":1442592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔 改不了吃屎","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:52:29.000Z","uid":64003,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"caa11385af184e52457ed0835a047550823fd6e4","tid":1442592,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"連登仔最鍾意啲咩？無錯 就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打飛機</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有女 就打曬飛機話要屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有快閃 就打曬飛機話撚到啲狗氹氹轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人屌保安 就打曬飛機話保安好驚無利是收<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打飛機還打飛機 無錯 你係可以射到一地都係 好撚爽<br />\n但打完之後你仲係連女神嘅手仔都掂唔到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地追求嘅唔只係一時三刻嘅快感<br />\n所以要諗吓你所做嘢嘅本身意義</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快閃運動 </span></span></strong><br />\n快閃嘅目標係撚狗之餘 又唔會有手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但尋日嘅快閃似乎係撚緊自己同其他人<br />\n喺荃灣 有師奶自發清理路障<br />\n喺荔枝角 有九巴職員協助指揮交通<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但尋晚啲狗都係快閃嚟 快閃去<br />\n工作量似乎冇乜點多到</strong></span><br />\n計吓成本同效益 就知佢唔係幾抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以喺哩個時候 我地唔應該打飛機話撚狗撚得幾咁成功<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼篇</span></span><br />\n而家有鬼跟住大家 令到啲狗可以預知到快閃黨嘅行動<br />\n喺快閃黨去到之前就有狗喺到部署 撚唔到狗 只撚到自己<br />\n因此 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>慾要撚狗 必先驅鬼</strong></span><br />\n可以試下無意義咁上車落車 或者喺非轉車站商討策略<br />\n如果有人全程跟住曬 咁佢係鬼嘅機會都幾大<br />\n捉到鬼要點樣處置就視乎各位嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">哨兵篇</span></span><br />\n我地嘅建築師落場嘅時候會專心做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起完嘢都好攰 想喺㗎車到抖吓<br />\n未必有精力去留意身邊嘅人同事<br />\n所以我地要哨兵去做指揮<br />\n哨兵要良好觀察力、分析力、判斷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要識得捉鬼 要知幾時攻、幾時守<br />\n喺快閃期間 佢地要分佈喺各個街口<br />\n睇吓有冇狗 或者其他特別嘢<br />\n如果有狗 記得要通報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咩狗 幾多隻 喺邊到</strong></span><br />\n而唔係一味話「有狗 快啲走」<br />\n<br />\n快閃黨需要審慎評估來緊幾次嘅行動效益<br />\n然後決定短時間內繼唔繼續快閃<br />\n識收 識放 先至係若水啊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推文策略</span></span></strong><br />\n熱門嘅po 再一次證明連登仔有幾鍾意打飛機<br />\n係 通宵屌保安係幾有趣 但笑完都幫唔到抗爭啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n與其ff保安無利是收嘅嘴臉 不如ff吓被補義士有幾慘<br />\n佢地先係同伴 先值得我地花心神落去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>推完飛機po 記得推返義士po</strong></span><br />\n比佢地知道 佢地並唔係condom 我地個個都咁撐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義士無分貴賤 尖沙咀路人被捕當然具爭議<br />\n但黃埔義士捨己救人 用身體換來其他手足有更多時間離開<br />\n哩種精神唔係更應記一功咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅行動都開始被人封住<br />\n要開拓新方向先可以繼續行落去<br />\n有巴打提到嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>商場集會</strong></span>、<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同休班狗開party</span></strong> 等等<br />\n都係一啲可行而成效值得期待嘅出路<br />\n最後希望大家反思一下<br />\n我地嘅行動係為咗啲咩<br />\n點樣先爭取到五大訴求<br />\n慎記<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> 對準政權 莫走歪路</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628b960a02eae81034711524b3467b5e0ba4a8c6","tid":1442592,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjQ517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XjQ517.jpg&h=8be1ffb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【求置頂】我係811港島東集會搞手，請大家冇野做就黎維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(冇人講)今日去深水埗!!!!唔好上淘寶！推爆我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19</a><br />\n<br />\n[求今日置頂] 811港島東要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[811] 深水埗 港島東 機場和你飛final call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e0b5b330921f05d3a6048447268a686d6562f96a","tid":1442592,"uid":293698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29767765f56f41a1e6ed1cd2e5f6d58d6c32d889","tid":1442592,"uid":90073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"借黎PO<br />\n<br />\n[純學術討論] 發夢期間前裂線問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441905</a>"},{"pid":"0215273beb5ed83c35bed2d0411f746dd8592518","tid":1442592,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"應該揾指定兩三個負責哨兵．要佢地不同區域，以免收到錯誤情報"},{"pid":"29d05840e8153cf939c4592239bf247040324022","tid":1442592,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0215273beb5ed83c35bed2d0411f746dd8592518","tid":1442592,"uid":196006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T